      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OAKLEY LANE (2) was narrowly beaten when placing two back but missed the frame latest finishing fourth (16.65) in a Maiden at The Gardens. Likely to improve sharply this time. ZIPPING GIDEY (8) is a Leeanne Goodwin-trained newcomer by Zipping Kyrgios out of Zipping Zarbo with no trial form to work with. Betting to provide the best guide to her chances. ROCKIN' MIA (3) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (17.90) at this track behind Where's The Luck in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. LAST ROLEX (1) makes debut for the Denis Solomon kennel. Drawn well and should get her chance. Profiles well so watch market closely.",
